a: Yes, Observe unnatural specular highlights: they may smear, flicker, or appear static, inconsistent with lighting and head movement. Note fine detail smearing: skin pores, hairs, and subtle wrinkles often appear blurred, overly smooth, or lack natural crispness, indicative of neural rendering artifacts.
